{"_path":"/trail/t014","_dir":"trail","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"林梢步道","description":null,"image":null,"sequence":14,"category":"五股","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"健康休閒"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-03-30T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"林梢步道"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"林梢步道"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"步道簡介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"步道簡介"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"林梢步道起點位於觀音山生態園區入口左側，終點為凌雲禪寺開山院，全長約 800 公尺，全線以鋼構棧橋構築，平穩舒暢，是條小而美的精巧步道。整條步道宛如穿梭林間的空中廊道，仰可觀樹林頂層之堂奧，俯可見綠波樹浪層層堆疊，盎然新綠讓人沉浸在林梢的芬多精之中恣意漫步。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"步道第一段是長約 400 公尺的無障礙步道，地勢較為高亢，可遠眺林口台地櫛比鱗次的高樓大廈。沿途林木蒼翠茂盛，有山黃麻、大榕樹、早期供做木屐或便當盒的鴨掌木（江某），及大家耳熟能詳的油桐。逢花開季節時，桐花宛如飛雪，灑落一地的浪漫。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第二段步道位於地勢較低的林內，需行約二層樓高的階梯下至棧道，蓊鬱翠綠的樹林、枝幹彎曲的大樹隨風搖擺，好像在揮手招呼，歡迎著每位遊人的到來。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地址： 248 新北市五股區凌雲路三段 130 號"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"自行開車"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自行開車"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文化一路右轉仁愛路, 再走粉寮路。粉寮路部分路段較窄，但仍維持雙向通車。在五林路接民義路時須採直行往觀音山方向。民義路二段就可達觀音山遊客中心。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由 A7 開車約 30 分鐘就能到達，在觀音山遊客中心有多處停車場。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"公共運輸"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公共運輸"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不建議使用大眾運輸前往，換車時間太長。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"相關介紹"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相關介紹"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"健行筆記: "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://hiking.biji.co/index.php?q=trail&act=detail&id=107"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"林梢步道"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"t014-01.jpeg","src":"/images/trail/t014-01.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"林梢步道","depth":2,"text":"林梢步道","children":[{"id":"步道簡介","depth":3,"text":"步道簡介"},{"id":"自行開車","depth":3,"text":"自行開車"},{"id":"公共運輸","depth":3,"text":"公共運輸"},{"id":"相關介紹","depth":3,"text":"相關介紹"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:trail:t014.md","_source":"content","_file":"trail/t014.md","_extension":"md"}